    • Olympus / Fujifilm

    And more cameras with similar sizes.

    Dyazo Camera Case

    Compatible with most of the DSLR

    Our shockproof insert camera case is a portable, dependable shoulder bag for taking pictures while you're out and about.

    Ensure the portability and safety of your mirror less camera and lenses.

    Dyazo Camera Bag

    • Dimension : External 26'' x 20'' x 15'' Cms.
    • Internal Dimension 25" x19 " x 15 "
    • The camera bag has two belt loops integrated into the back so you may wear it o for convenience
    • Fits 1 camera +1 spare lens + mobile phone + filter + SD card.

    Soft Firm Carry Handel

    When carrying, the ventilation structure improves air circulation and efficiently dissipates heat.

    zipper pocket Front

    The camera bag's front zipper pocket can be used to store a small book, cards, chargers, an SD card box, a filter cloth, or a cleaning kit.

    Two-way Superior Zinc Alloy Zipper

    A top-notch zinc alloy two-way zipper

    Adjustable Shoulder Strap Length

    The shoulder strap for the camera bag can be adjusted .

    Water Resistant Material

    The material is constructed of 900D high-density waterproof polyester, which is effective in repelling dust and water splashes.

    Imagine shock-resistant dividers

    Thick material dividers High-elastic PE dividers that are shockproof and fall-proof are a superb choice for protecting your pricey equipment.
